* Iron Raptor looked past Liono and at the door behind him, it was a typical 
door besides the fact that the two pictures of a Lion and Dragon were on it. 
She looked back at her commander and sighed, it had been a long day and she 
had used a lot of energy in the earlier battle. Her energy level was stable 
but nowhere near the needed capacity in order to activate her Second Beast 
Mode again, if needed.
Iron Raptor looked at Liono, at least she knew that he was pleased with the 
battle's outcome.*
